GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 1st August, 2001.
10 Sravana, 1922(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 1st August, 2001
Shri Digvijay Singh assumed the charge of the office of Minister of State in the Ministry
of Railways. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of Minister of State in the
Ministry of Commerce and Industry.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
